<verse number="18" style="v" />See, Yahweh's eye is on those who fear him,</para>

<para style="q1">on those who count on his covenant faithfulness</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />to deliver their lives from death</para>

<para style="q1">and to keep them alive in times of famine.</para>
